Tout son corps est fait de lames.
Si une lame smousse, il va laiguiser
contre une pierre au bord dune rivire.

Blades comprise this Pokmons entire
body. If battling dulls the blades, it
sharpens them on stones by the river.

by sinking the blades that cover their

lsst es seine Klingen schwingend ertnen.

It follows Bisharps orders to a tee when it

Incalza il nemico con le lame che ha sul corpo,

It uses river stones to maintain the cutting edges

Con i suoi simili forma gruppi capeggiati da
un Bisharp. Si allena quotidianamente sognando

A pack of these Pokmon forms to serve a
Bisharp boss. Each Pawniard trains diligently,
dreaming of one day taking the lead.
